public final class RoundRobinAccessor<T extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.JdbcOperations>
extends ImmutableAccessor<T,org.springframework.jdbc.core.namedparam.SqlParameterSource>

Round-robin collection accessor. Copies provided collection into inner immutable one on creation. Element is chosen in circular order ignoring provided parameter. Thread-safe.

Author:
alexkasko Date: 6/11/12
